        "rich_text_ND9GCy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Exploring Lucira's Collections: A Price Guide for Every Woman",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Exploring Lucira's Collections: A Price Guide for Every Woman</h2><p>Understanding the general factors is one thing, but seeing actual price ranges helps answer the question of how much does a diamond ring cost in India.<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" Lucira Jewelry\"> Lucira Jewelry</a> offers a wide array of designs to suit every taste and milestone.</p>",
            "custom_id": "Exploring"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_cPbJNJ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How Much Does Diamond Ring Cost in India for Female: Engagement & Wedding Styles",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>How Much Does Diamond Ring Cost in India for Female: Engagement & Wedding Styles</h3><p>For those special moments, the question of how much does a diamond ring cost in India for females is paramount. Lucira's collections span timeless<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-for-women\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">engagement rings for women</span></a>, glamorous halos, modern 'Toi et Moi' rings, and elegant eternity bands. We believe luxury should be accessible, and our pricing reflects that commitment. The cost for a diamond ring in India for women can vary based on design complexity and diamond size.</p>",
            "custom_id": "how-much"
          }
        },
