        "rich_text_K3x6NL": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Choosing Your Metal: Recycled Gold and Its Impact on Price",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Choosing Your Metal: Recycled Gold and Its Impact on Price</h2><p>Lucira primarily uses 18K gold (yellow, white, rose) and platinum. Gold is a timeless and popular choice, while platinum is a denser, rarer, and typically more expensive metal known for its durability. We are proud to use recycled gold in our creations, a sustainable choice that doesn't compromise on quality. Every piece of Lucira jewelry comes with a BIS Hallmark, assuring you of its purity and authenticity. If you’d like to explore these materials and designs in person, visit the<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/chembur-store\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Chembur Lucira Store</span></a> to experience our craftsmanship up close.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_tQzHkm": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Your Personal Shopping Experience with Lucira Jewelry",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Your Personal Shopping Experience with Lucira Jewelry</h2><p>We've redefined the jewelry shopping experience to be as transparent and personal as our jewelry. We provide expert guidance every step of the way as you decide on your purchase.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qGtXEn": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Expert Guidance via Video Call Consultations and WhatsApp Assistance",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Expert Guidance via Video Call Consultations and WhatsApp Assistance</h3><p>Shopping for a diamond ring from home has never been easier or more reassuring. You can book a free video call with our jewelry experts to see pieces up close, ask detailed questions, and receive personalized styling advice. For quick queries, our WhatsApp assistance provides instant support. For those in Mumbai, our Experience Store offers a chance to interact with our collections in person. You can also explore exclusive designs like our elegant<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/mens-engagement-rings\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">engagement rings for men</span></a>, crafted with the same precision and sophistication Lucira is known for.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3fBN74": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion - The Final Lucira Tip",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion: Your Yes, Your forever </h2><p>Choosing an engagement ring is both emotional and practical, a mix of instinct and intention. The right one won't just look beautiful; it will feel like home.</p><p>Whether it's the confidence of the radiant solitaire, the modern geometry of the princess cut or the tenderness of the heart shaped ring, each piece in Lucira Jewelry’s collection is designed to capture one thing, that perfect unforgettable yes.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion"
          }
        }
